com.iplanet.ums

Interface IClassResolver


  • public interface IClassResolver
    Interface for a class that can resolve the Java class to instantiate for a specific collection of attributes.
    See Also:
    TemplateManager

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Class resolve(String id, AttrSet set)
      Resolves a set of attributes to a subclass of PersistentObject and returns the class for it.

    • Method Detail

      • resolve

        Class resolve(String id,
            AttrSet set)
        Resolves a set of attributes to a subclass of PersistentObject and returns the class for it.
        Parameters:
        id - ID of the entry
        set - a set of attributes of an object
        Returns:
        a class for a corresponding object, or null if no class could be resolved
